title: Week 5 Studs & Duds + Taysom Tortures MIke, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/10
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a Week 5 review of the biggest studs and duds! Which studs will keep performing for fantasy football teams, and which duds are cause for concern? Plus, lots of injury news, and the Week 5 edition of Monday Punday. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 10th, 2022.
